Package com.googlecode.starrating

Interface Summary
StarRatingConstants Star Rating constants
 

Class Summary
RemoveButton A JLabel that acts like a button for clearing the rate (sets it to 0.0) The label has a default size of 20x20 with an empty border
A StarMouseAdapter can be added for receiving mouse events
StarRating StarRating Class
StarRating is a JPanel that holds images of half stars
The rate ranges from 0 to the number of stars with a step of 0.5.
StarTableCellEditor A StarRating table cell editor
StarTableCellRenderer A StarRating cell renderer
ValueLabel A label displaying the StarRating rate.
